    "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong></p>\n<p>We specialized in providing a full range of recruitment placement.</p>\n<p>Our specialized recruitment service division include IT, Finance &amp; Accounting, HR &amp; Administration, Sales &amp; Marketing, Logistics &amp; Supply Chain.</p>\n<p>Our parent company, Combuilder Pte Ltd, was incorporated since 1999.&nbsp; Our business include the large scale of software development for MRT projects &amp; facility management for town councils.&nbsp; We also provide IT manpower outsourcing to multi-national companies and government sectors.</p>\n<p><strong>What We Provide</strong></p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Permanent Placement</p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Contract Placement</p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Temporary Placement</p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Payroll Services</p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Work Pass Application</p>\n<p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Focus on delivering the right people</p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Affordable and cost-effective services</p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Maintain long lasting relationship</p>\n<p>•&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Talent Management</p>\n<p><strong>Maestro HR Pte Ltd</strong></p>\n<p><strong>16C8462</strong></p>",
